datree test KUBERNETES_FILE_NAME.yaml
datree test FOLDER_NAME/*.yaml

[Authenticating - Datree CLI connects to account using an token, It store the authentication details in "~/.datree/config.yaml" file.]
datree config set token TOKEN_VALUE

[To disable the Datree CLI account connection, don't want scans to communicate with Datree's servers.]
datree config set offline local
